article.contentHtml: if(msg.indexOf("소스제작")==0){ var m = msg.substr(5) var a = m.split(" ")[0] var b = m.split("라고 하면 ")[1] switch(a){ case "만약": replier.reply("if(msg.trim()==\""+m.split("라고 하면")[0].replace(/만약 /g,"")+"\"){replier.reply(\""+b.split("라고 답한다")[0]+"\")}") break; case "파싱": var p = m.split("사이트:")[1].split("범위")[0]; var s = m.split("범위:")[1].split("~")[0]; var s2 = m.split("~")[1].split("까지")[0]; replier.reply("if(msg.trim()==\"파싱\"){\n"+"var u = Utils.getWebText(\""+p+"\")\n"+"var a = \""+s+"\"+u.split(\""+s+"\")[1];\n"+"var b = a.split(\""+s2+"\")[0].replace(/(<([^>]+)>)/g,\"\") + \""+s2+"\"\n replier.reply(b)}"); break; } }
